<br>
I didnt see a plat limit nor have any idea what your guild is capable of, so im tryin to choose some easy to acquire items. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=lourdib>Lourdib</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/30/03 12:06:16 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4945.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/p_ac.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: New Armor Suggestions...</span><hr size=1> Sorry for the lack of info...  Helanic is almsot impossible to come by on SH.  I have about 40K to spend and we are a solid tier2 guild in PoP. <p><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Lourdin Ironforge</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
